					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2250198#post-2803147</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2250198/scp-2659#post-2803147</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 27 Apr 2017 14:56:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>RJB_R</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1229263</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I wish this had a greater focus on what this entity does to the souls but I can't deny that it got a reaction out of me. I kind of wanted to downvote because as it reads it feels like a thing what kills <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">you</span> whales but I feel like I can get behind this as something the Foundation is still attempting to study/documentation for a level 1 researcher.<br /> I still would like to see just a bit more, just a hint, of what it's doing with these souls but I enjoyed reading it as-is. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
